<P>
Heartfelt gratitude fo NBC for its presentation of Franco Zeffirelli's 
magnificent "Jesus of Nazareth." This miniseries offered my family a treasured 
view of the real meaning of Easter, a tapestry of eternal love triumphant over 
death. The thoughtful exclusion of commercials during the conclusion was 
especially appreciated. 
</P>
<P>
Claire Haller, Blue Jay 
