<TEXT>
<P>
Meanwhile, out at Universal Studios, Fla., casting is under way on another 
comics-inspired project -- "Swamp Thing," the TV series. 
</P>
<P>
For syndication from Universal (no air date has been announced), it's produced 
by Boris Malden, Joseph Stefano ("Outer Limits") and Adam Rifkin. 
</P>
<P>
Dick Durock, who played the title character in the two "Swamp Thing" movies, 
will reprise his role as the leafy hero. Pat H. Broeske 
</P>
