<P>
Photo, Dutch Treat: Windmills along a canal in the central Netherlands are 
illuminated to mark the country's liberation from Nazi rule in May, 1945. 
Associated Press 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
<TYPE>
<P>
Wild Art; Wire 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA042990-0032 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 211141 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
April 29, 1990, Sunday, Bulldog Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
