<HEADLINE>
<P>
SHANGHAI EXECUTES SIX CHINESE KILLER-ROBBERS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Reuters 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
BEIJING 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Six Chinese who killed and robbed to pay their gambling debts have been 
executed in Shanghai, according to a report reaching Beijing Friday. 
</P>
<P>
The Shanghai Liberation Daily said the men had killed seven people and tied up 
the 3-year-old daughter of one of the victims. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
