<P>
Travel; Part L; Page 20; Column 6; Travel Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
45 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
POOLING THEIR RESOURCES 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Believe me, the pool at the Kamari Hotel on Santorini is not the only pool on 
the island, as Jeff Halstead's article says ("Island of Santorini is One of 
Greece's Loveliest," April 1). The best pool is at the Atlantis Villas Hotel in 
Oia. 
</P>
<P>
JIM HERMANN 
</P>
<P>
Beverly Hills 
</P>
</TEXT>
