<P>
From "Body in Flames/Cuerpo en Llamas" (Chronicle Books: $8.95, paper; 107 pp.; 
0-87701-718-2); translated by Francisco Aragon. Alarcon is a third-generation 
Californian who spent much of his childhood in Mexico. Winner of Danforth and 
