<P>
** "FREEDOM" NEIL YOUNG WARNER REPRISE VIDEO VIDEOCASSETTE ($19.98): A PERIODIC 
SURVEY OF POP-RELATED LASER DISCS, BOOKS AND VIDEOCASSETTES. RATED ON A SCALE 
OF ONE (POOR) TO FIVE STARS (A CLASSIC.) 
