<BYLINE>
<P>
By ROBERT HILBURN 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Young may not sing for Miller or for Bud, but he apparently doesn't have any 
reservations about lending his music and name to lazy-concept videos. Instead 
of an original or even definitive showcase of the music from last year's highly 
acclaimed "Freedom" album, this modest 30-minute package features 
straightforward footage of Young performing seven songs, ranging from his old 
