SOCIAL ELITE'S VALUES AT WORK IN PARTY SCENE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Jeannine Stein's "Party Politics" (April 15) spotlights the shallow values of 
the powerful social elite. 
</P>
<P>
