<DOCNO> LA042990-0141 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 211442 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
April 29, 1990, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Real Estate; Part K; Page 16; Column 5; Real Estate Desk 
</P>
