paint mixing attachment, PATRICK LYNCH / Los Angeles Times ; Drawing, hole saw, 
PATRICK LYNCH / Los Angeles Times ; Drawing, mount drill, PATRICK LYNCH / Los 
Angeles Times ; Drawing, grinding wheel, PATRICK LYNCH / Los Angeles Times ; 
Drawing, drill attachments, PATRICK LYNCH / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
