<HEADLINE>
<P>
BETTING WITH BOB 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Times handicapper Bob Mieszerski lost $36 when Tartas, his first horse in his 
$6 triple, ran second in the seventh race to Zayyani. Bob, who started with a 
mythical $1,000 bankroll, is now at $844. 
</P>
<P>
Bob's bet today is a $30 win parlay from Atrevida in the fourth to Smoke Jumper 
in the sixth. 
</P>
<P>
Saturday's Bankroll $880 
</P>
<P>
Saturday's Loss $36 
</P>
<P>
Current Bankroll $844 
</P>
