<HEADLINE>
<P>
CS FULLERTON SPLITS SOFTBALL DOUBLEHEADER 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Cal State Fullerton gained a split with Cal Poly Pomona in a Big West 
Conference softball doubleheader Saturday at Pomona. 
</P>
<P>
Fullerton (42-17, 20-9 in conference) won the first game, 2-0, on run-scoring 
singles by Missy Coombes and Charlotte Wiley. Pomona (27-30, 10-18) won the 
second game, 1-0, behind the one-hit pitching of Bonnie Ebenkamp. 
</P>
<P>
In California Collegiate Athletic Assn. softball: 
</P>
<P>
Cal State Bakersfield 2-1, Chapman 1-0 -- Trina Honea had Chapman's (36-17, 
7-11) only run batted in at Bakersfield (33-11, 11-7). 
</P>
</TEXT>
