Angeles Times; Photo, Rich Goldberg is the founder of the American Roundball 
Corp. He's turned out such basketball names as Chris Mills and Sean Higgins. 
GEORGE WILHELM / Los Angeles Times; Photo, Chris Mills left Kentucky after the 
school was placed on probation. He transferred to Arizona, where he will be 
eligible to play next season. Los Angeles Times; Photo, (Bulldog Edition) 
